title: junior Front-end developer
whoTitle: Front-end developer with keen eye for design
whoText: As a front-end developer I am always looking to find the perfect balance between functionality and design. Thanks to my design skills and my experience as a system administrator, I am able to work on a broad range of subjects in the area of of webdevelopment.
whatText: Ideally I am looking for a place where the other developers find joy in educating their junior developers. Overall I would say I thrive best in an envirnment where everyone is eager to learn and share knowledge.
